I enter the phone number "694136000" in the input
I click on "LET'S GO" button

I enter the password "#Test123" in the input
I click on "SIGN IN" button
I check that the "Notification Permission Screen" is displayed
I click on "CONTINUE" button
I check that the "Location Permission Flow Screen" is displayed
I click on "CONTINUE" button
I close "Tell Us What You Think Pane"
I skip linking my card

I check that the location services are enabled on real device
I check that the "Enable location" warning is displayed
I check that the "We can't find you" text is displayed
I mock the location of the device to "NORWAY_NOT_AT_STATION"
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Profile" tab is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "NORWAY_NOT_AT_STATION" station

I enter the "Latitude" in the input
I enter the "Longitude" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I check if "Car Wash" advertisement is displayed
I close and open application
I make sure that the location is set correctly
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I swipe on the home screen down to see "How it Works" button
I swipe on the device screen to the "DOWN"
I click on "CAR WASH" tab
I make sure that the "CAR WASH" tab is in the default state
I click on Car Wash "CHECK PROGRAMS" button

I check that the "Car wash Subscription Screen" is displayed
I click on "SELECT PLAN" button of "DELUX SESONG" Car Wash Subscription
I check that the "Enter your license plate Screen" is displayed
I enter the plate number "NO78DLbG" in the input
I click on "COUNTRY" selector
I click on "NORWAY" country button
I click on "TOS" checkbox
I click on "CONTINUE" button
I check that the "Order summary Screen" is displayed
I get the text from the "VEHICLE" text
I check that the application text: "NO78DLBG NO" is equals to expected value: "NO78DLBG NO"
I click on "CONTINUE TO PAYMENT" button
I check that the "Location Permissions Screen" is displayed
I click on "CONTINUE" button
I check that the "Welcome to Car Wash Subscription Screen" is displayed
I click on "BACK TO HOME SCREEN" button

I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "CAR WASH SUBSCRIPTION" tab
I check that the "Manage Subscription Screen" is displayed
I get the text from the "YOUR SUBSCRIPTION" text

I get the text from the "CAR REGISTRATION" text
